{{Politics of Benin}}
'''Alliance for Social Democracy''' ({{Lang-fr|Alliance pour la Social-Démocratie}}) is a political party in [[Benin]] led by [[Robert Dossou]].<ref>{{cite book |last1=Houngnikpo |first1=Mathurin C.  |last2=Decalo |first2=Samuel |date=2013 |title=Historical Dictionary of Benin |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0yGPTsRubWEC&pg=PA145 |publisher=Rowman & Littlefield |page=145 |isbn=0810871718 |access-date=28 July 2015}}</ref> The ASD was legally recognized on 12 October 1990.

