'''Odqan''' is a fire spirit in the [[Shamanism|shamanistic]] traditions of [[Mongolia]]. 

He is usually described as a red coloured humanoid, riding a brown [[goat]]. His female counterpart is Yal-un eke, the 'fire mother'.

